  and replace the img-tags in the body).
- Make full forum pdfs with internal links.
- Add internal links to each message and a ToC (like shown in
  http://www.tecnick.com/public/code/cp_dpage.php?aiocp_dp=tcpdf_examples,
  No. 45).
- Add file attachments to pdf (like shown in
  http://www.tecnick.com/public/code/cp_dpage.php?aiocp_dp=tcpdf_examples,
  No. 41).
